<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<meta name="theme-color" content="#0a0a0a"/>
<title>Kumpulan Doa — Zero Ichiro</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@400;600;700&family=Lora:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;1,400&family=Amiri:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
:root {
  --gold:#c9a84c; --gold-l:#e8c97a; --gold-d:#8a6c2a;
  --bg:#0a0a0a; --bg2:#111; --bg3:#1a1a1a; --bg4:#222;
  --text:#e8dcc0; --text-d:#9a8a6a;
  --border:rgba(201,168,76,0.2); --border-b:rgba(201,168,76,0.5);
  --cream:#f5e9c8;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent}
body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:'Lora',Georgia,serif;min-height:100vh;overflow-x:hidden}
body::before{content:'';position:fixed;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% -10%,rgba(201,168,76,0.07) 0%,transparent 70%);pointer-events:none;z-index:0}

/* HEADER */
header{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:200;background:rgba(10,10,10,0.97);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);backdrop-filter:blur(16px)}
.hdr{max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;padding:14px 16px 8px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center}
.brand-title{font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gold);letter-spacing:2px}
.brand-sub{font-size:11px;color:var(--text-d);font-style:italic;letter-spacing:1px;margin-top:2px}
.hdr-btns{display:flex;gap:7px}
.icon-btn{background:var(--bg3);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:7px 11px;color:var(--text-d);cursor:pointer;font-size:14px;transition:all .2s;font-family:inherit;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px}
.icon-btn:hover{border-color:var(--gold-d);color:var(--gold-l)}
.icon-btn.active{background:var(--gold);color:var(--bg);border-color:var(--gold);font-weight:bold}

/* TABS */
.tabs{max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;padding:8px 16px 10px;display:flex;gap:6px;overflow-x:auto;scrollbar-width:none}
.tabs::-webkit-scrollbar{display:none}
.tab{padding:6px 13px;border-radius:20px;border:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--bg3);color:var(--text-d);cursor:pointer;font-size:12px;font-family:'Lora',serif;white-space:nowrap;transition:all .2s;letter-spacing:.4px}
.tab:hover{border-color:var(--gold-d);color:var(--gold-l)}
.tab.active{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gold),var(--gold-d));border-color:var(--gold);color:var(--bg);font-weight:600}

/* AI SEARCH SECTION */
.ai-section{max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;padding:14px 16px 4px;position:relative;z-index:1}
.ai-label{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:10px}
.ai-badge{font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:2px;color:var(--gold);text-transform:uppercase;background:rgba(201,168,76,0.1);border:1px solid var(--gold-d);border-radius:20px;padding:3px 10px}
.ai-desc{font-size:11px;color:var(--text-d);font-style:italic}
.ai-box{display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-end}
.ai-textarea{flex:1;background:var(--bg3);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:12px 14px;color:var(--text);font-size:14px;font-family:'Lora',serif;resize:none;outline:none;min-height:52px;max-height:120px;transition:border-color .2s;line-height:1.5}
.ai-textarea:focus{border-color:var(--gold-d)}
.ai-textarea::placeholder{color:var(--text-d)}
.ai-send{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gold),var(--gold-d));border:none;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;cursor:pointer;color:var(--bg);font-size:18px;transition:all .2s;flex-shrink:0;font-weight:bold}
.ai-send:hover{transform:scale(1.05);box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(201,168,76,0.3)}
.ai-send:disabled{opacity:.5;cursor:not-allowed;transform:none}

/* AI RESULT */
.ai-result{max-width:700px;margin:10px auto 0;padding:0 16px;position:relative;z-index:1}
.ai-result-card{background:linear-gradient(145deg,#0f0f0f,var(--bg3));border:1px solid var(--border-b);border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden}
.ai-result-header{padding:12px 16px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);background:rgba(201,168,76,0.04)}
.ai-result-icon{font-size:16px}
.ai-result-label{font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:2px;color:var(--gold);text-transform:uppercase}
.ai-result-body{padding:16px}

/* Loading dots */
.loading-dots{display:flex;gap:5px;justify-content:center;padding:20px}
.dot{width:7px;height:7px;background:var(--gold);border-radius:50%;animation:bounce .8s infinite}
.dot:nth-child(2){animation-delay:.15s}
.dot:nth-child(3){animation-delay:.3s}
@keyframes bounce{0%,100%{transform:translateY(0);opacity:.4}50%{transform:translateY(-8px);opacity:1}}

/* DOA DISPLAY (shared for both local and AI result) */
.doa-arabic{font-family:'Amiri',serif;font-size:23px;direction:rtl;text-align:right;color:var(--cream);line-height:2.2;padding:14px 16px;background:rgba(201,168,76,0.04);border-radius:10px;border-right:2px solid var(--gold-d);margin-bottom:12px}
.doa-latin{font-family:'Lora',serif;font-size:13px;font-style:italic;color:var(--gold-l);line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:8px;opacity:.85}
.sep{height:1px;background:var(--border);margin:8px 0}
.doa-id{font-family:'Lora',serif;font-size:13.5px;color:var(--text);line-height:1.75;font-style:italic;margin-bottom:12px;opacity:.85}
.doa-source{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:4px 11px;border-radius:20px;font-size:11px;font-family:'Cinzel',serif;letter-spacing:.5px}
.src-quran{background:rgba(201,168,76,0.08);border:1px solid var(--gold-d);color:var(--gold-l)}
.src-hadis{background:rgba(201,168,76,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.25);color:var(--text-d)}
.doa-title-ai{font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:13px;color:var(--gold-l);letter-spacing:.8px;margin-bottom:10px}

/* AI multi-result */
.ai-multi-item{margin-bottom:20px;padding-bottom:20px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.ai-multi-item:last-child{border-bottom:none;margin-bottom:0;padding-bottom:0}

/* DIVIDER */
.divider{max-width:700px;margin:14px auto 0;padding:0 16px;position:relative;z-index:1}
.divider-line{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;opacity:.4}
.divider-line::before,.divider-line::after{content:'';flex:1;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,var(--gold-d),transparent)}
.divider-text{font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:3px;color:var(--gold);text-transform:uppercase;white-space:nowrap}

/* LOCAL SEARCH */
.local-search{max-width:700px;margin:12px auto 0;padding:0 16px;position:relative;z-index:1}
.search-wrap{position:relative}
.search-icon{position:absolute;left:13px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);color:var(--text-d);font-size:13px;pointer-events:none}
.search-input{width:100%;padding:10px 12px 10px 34px;background:var(--bg3);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;color:var(--text);font-size:13.5px;font-family:'Lora',serif;outline:none;transition:border-color .2s}
.search-input:focus{border-color:var(--gold-d)}
.search-input::placeholder{color:var(--text-d)}

/* CONTENT */
.content{max-width:700px;margin:12px auto 0;padding:0 16px 50px;position:relative;z-index:1}
.section-lbl{text-align:center;font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:3px;color:var(--gold-d);text-transform:uppercase;padding:4px 0 12px}

/* CARD */
.card{background:linear-gradient(145deg,var(--bg2),var(--bg3));border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;margin-bottom:9px;overflow:hidden;transition:border-color .2s,box-shadow .2s;animation:fadeUp .35s ease both}
.card:hover{border-color:var(--border-b);box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(201,168,76,0.07)}
.card-hdr{padding:13px 15px;cursor:pointer;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;user-select:none}
.card-left{flex:1;min-width:0}
.card-title{font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:600;color:var(--gold-l);letter-spacing:.7px;margin-bottom:7px}
.arabic-prev{font-family:'Amiri',serif;font-size:19px;direction:rtl;text-align:right;color:var(--cream);line-height:1.9;opacity:.9}
.card-right{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-end;gap:7px;flex-shrink:0}
.bm-btn{background:none;border:none;font-size:16px;cursor:pointer;color:var(--text-d);padding:2px;transition:all .2s;line-height:1}
.bm-btn.saved{color:var(--gold);text-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(201,168,76,.5)}
.arrow{color:var(--text-d);font-size:11px;transition:transform .25s;display:block}
.arrow.open{transform:rotate(180deg)}
.card-body{padding:0 15px 16px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);display:none}
.card-body.open{display:block}
.gold-line{width:36px;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,var(--gold-d),transparent);margin:11px auto}

.empty{text-align:center;padding:50px 20px;color:var(--text-d)}
.empty-icon{font-size:40px;margin-bottom:12px;opacity:.4}

.footer{text-align:center;padding:20px 16px 14px;font-size:10px;font-family:'Cinzel',serif;letter-spacing:2px;color:var(--text-d);text-transform:uppercase;opacity:.4;position:relative;z-index:1}

@keyframes fadeUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(13px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
@keyframes fadeIn{from{opacity:0}to{opacity:1}}
.fade-in{animation:fadeIn .4s ease both}

/* Error */
.ai-error{padding:16px;text-align:center;color:#e88;font-size:13px;font-style:italic}

/* Streaming text */
.streaming::after{content:'▋';color:var(--gold);animation:blink .7s infinite}
@keyframes blink{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:0}}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="hdr">
    <div>
      <div class="brand-title">🤲 Kumpulan Doa</div>
      <div class="brand-sub">Al-Qur'an & Hadis · Zero Ichiro</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hdr-btns">
      <button class="icon-btn" id="bmToggle" onclick="toggleBmView()">☆ <span id="bmCount">0</span></button>
      <button class="icon-btn" id="darkBtn" onclick="toggleDark()">☀</button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="tabs" id="tabs"></div>
</header>

<!-- AI SEARCH -->
<div class="ai-section">
  <div class="ai-label">
    <span class="ai-badge">✦ AI Search</span>
    <span class="ai-desc">Tanya Claude untuk carikan doa, bacaan, atau shalawat</span>
  </div>
  <div class="ai-box">
    <textarea class="ai-textarea" id="aiInput" placeholder="Contoh: doa ketika gundah gulana, shalawat nariyah, doa sebelum bepergian jauh..." rows="1" oninput="autoResize(this)" onkeydown="handleKey(event)"></textarea>
    <button class="ai-send" id="aiBtn" onclick="searchAI()" title="Cari dengan AI">🔍</button>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="aiResult"></div>

<!-- DIVIDER -->
<div class="divider">
  <div class="divider-line"><span class="divider-text">Koleksi Doa</span></div>
</div>

<!-- LOCAL SEARCH -->
<div class="local-search">
  <div class="search-wrap">
    <span class="search-icon">🔍</span>
    <input class="search-input" id="localSearch" placeholder="Cari dalam koleksi..." oninput="renderCards()"/>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="content" id="content"></div>
<div class="footer">بَارَكَ اللهُ فِيكُم · Zero Ichiro</div>

<script>
const duas=[
  // ========== HARIAN ==========
  {id:1,cat:"harian",title:"Doa Sebelum Makan",
   arabic:"بِسْمِ اللَّهِ وَعَلَى بَرَكَةِ اللَّهِ",
   latin:"Bismillāhi wa 'alā barakātillāh.",
   id_text:"Dengan menyebut nama Allah dan atas berkah Allah.",
   source:"HR. Abu Dawud no. 3767",type:"hadis"},

  {id:2,cat:"harian",title:"Doa Sesudah Makan",
   arabic:"الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ الَّذِي أَطْعَمَنَا وَسَقَانَا وَجَعَلَنَا مُسْلِمِينَ",
   latin:"Alḥamdulillāhil-ladzī ath'amanā wa saqānā wa ja'alanā muslimīn.",
   id_text:"Segala puji bagi Allah yang telah memberi kami makan, minum, dan menjadikan kami orang-orang Muslim.",
   source:"HR. Abu Dawud no. 3850",type:"hadis"},

  {id:3,cat:"harian",title:"Doa Sebelum Tidur",
   arabic:"بِسْمِكَ اللَّهُمَّ أَمُوتُ وَأَحْيَا",
   latin:"Bismika Allāhumma amūtu wa aḥyā.",
   id_text:"Dengan nama-Mu ya Allah, aku mati dan aku hidup.",
   source:"HR. Bukhari no. 6324",type:"hadis"},

  {id:4,cat:"harian",title:"Doa Bangun Tidur",
   arabic:"الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ الَّذِي أَحْيَانَا بَعْدَ مَا أَمَاتَنَا وَإِلَيْهِ النُّشُورُ",
   latin:"Alḥamdulillāhil-ladzī aḥyānā ba'da mā amātanā wa ilaihin-nusyūr.",
   id_text:"Segala puji bagi Allah yang telah menghidupkan kami setelah mematikan kami, dan kepada-Nya lah kami dikembalikan.",
   source:"HR. Bukhari no. 6312",type:"hadis"},

  {id:5,cat:"harian",title:"Doa Keluar Rumah",
   arabic:"بِسْمِ اللَّهِ تَوَكَّلْتُ عَلَى اللَّهِ، وَلَا حَوْلَ وَلَا قُوَّةَ إِلَّا بِاللَّهِ",
   latin:"Bismillāhi, tawakkaltu 'alallāhi, wa lā ḥawla wa lā quwwata illā billāh.",
   id_text:"Dengan nama Allah, aku bertawakal kepada Allah. Tidak ada daya dan kekuatan melainkan dengan pertolongan Allah.",
   source:"HR. Abu Dawud no. 5095",type:"hadis"},

  {id:6,cat:"harian",title:"Doa Masuk Rumah",
   arabic:"اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي أَسْأَلُكَ خَيْرَ الْمَوْلِجِ وَخَيْرَ الْمَخْرَجِ، بِسْمِ اللَّهِ وَلَجْنَا، وَبِسْمِ اللَّهِ خَرَجْنَا، وَعَلَى اللَّهِ رَبِّنَا تَوَكَّلْنَا",
   latin:"Allāhumma innī as'aluka khayral-mawliji wa khayral-makhraj. Bismillāhi walajna, wa bismillāhi kharajnā, wa 'alallāhi rabbinā tawakkalnā.",
   id_text:"Ya Allah, sesungguhnya aku memohon kepada-Mu kebaikan tempat masuk dan kebaikan tempat keluar. Dengan nama Allah kami masuk, dengan nama Allah kami keluar, dan kepada Allah Tuhan kami, kami bertawakal.",
   source:"HR. Abu Dawud no. 5096",type:"hadis"},

  {id:7,cat:"harian",title:"Doa Naik Kendaraan",
   arabic:"بِسْمِ اللَّهِ، الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ، سُبْحَانَ الَّذِي سَخَّرَ لَنَا هَذَا وَمَا كُنَّا لَهُ مُقْرِنِينَ، وَإِنَّا إِلَى رَبِّنَا لَمُنقَلِبُونَ. الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ، الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ، الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ، اللَّهُ أَكْبَرُ، اللَّهُ أَكْبَرُ، اللَّهُ أَكْبَرُ، سُبْحَانَكَ اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي ظَلَمْتُ نَفْسِي فَاغْفِرْ لِي، فَإِنَّهُ لَا يَغْفِرُ الذُّنُوبَ إِلَّا أَنْتَ",
   latin:"Bismillāh, alḥamdulillāh. Subḥānal-ladzī sakhkhara lanā hādzā wa mā kunnā lahū muqrinīn, wa innā ilā rabbinā lamunqalibūn. Alḥamdulillāh, alḥamdulillāh, alḥamdulillāh. Allāhu akbar, Allāhu akbar, Allāhu akbar. Subḥānaka Allāhumma innī ẓalamtu nafsī faghfir lī, fa-innahū lā yaghfirudz-dzunūba illā anta.",
   id_text:"Dengan nama Allah, segala puji bagi Allah. Mahasuci Allah yang telah menundukkan kendaraan ini bagi kami, padahal kami sebelumnya tidak mampu menguasainya. Dan sesungguhnya kami akan kembali kepada Tuhan kami. Segala puji bagi Allah (3x). Allah Mahabesar (3x). Mahasuci Engkau ya Allah, sesungguhnya aku telah menganiaya diriku sendiri maka ampunilah aku, karena tidak ada yang dapat mengampuni dosa-dosa kecuali Engkau.",
   source:"HR. Abu Dawud no. 2602 & QS. Az-Zukhruf: 13-14",type:"hadis"},

  {id:8,cat:"harian",title:"Doa Masuk Kamar Mandi",
   arabic:"بِسْمِ اللَّهِ، اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي أَعُوذُ بِكَ مِنَ الْخُبُثِ وَالْخَبَائِثِ",
   latin:"Bismillāh. Allāhumma innī a'ūdzubika minal-khubutsi wal-khabā'its.",
   id_text:"Dengan nama Allah. Ya Allah, sesungguhnya aku berlindung kepada-Mu dari setan laki-laki dan setan perempuan.",
   source:"HR. Bukhari no. 142 & Muslim no. 375",type:"hadis"},

  {id:9,cat:"harian",title:"Doa Keluar Kamar Mandi",
   arabic:"غُفْرَانَكَ، الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ الَّذِي أَذْهَبَ عَنِّي الْأَذَى وَعَافَانِي",
   latin:"Ghufrānaka. Alḥamdulillāhil-ladzī adzhaba 'annil-adzā wa 'āfānī.",
   id_text:"Aku memohon ampunan-Mu. Segala puji bagi Allah yang telah menghilangkan penyakitku dan memberiku kesehatan.",
   source:"HR. Abu Dawud no. 30 & Ibn Majah no. 301",type:"hadis"},

  {id:10,cat:"harian",title:"Doa Bercermin",
   arabic:"اللَّهُمَّ أَنْتَ حَسَّنْتَ خَلْقِي فَحَسِّنْ خُلُقِي، وَحَرِّمْ وَجْهِي عَلَى النَّارِ",
   latin:"Allāhumma anta ḥassanta khalqī fa-ḥassin khuluqī, wa ḥarrim wajhī 'alan-nār.",
   id_text:"Ya Allah, sebagaimana Engkau telah memperindah rupaku, maka perindahlah pula akhlakku, dan haramkanlah wajahku dari api neraka.",
